There are two ways to run ansible command
1. by ansible
2. by ansible playbook

Ansible:
ansible <host> -a command
ansbile all -a "/sbin/reboot" -i inventory.txt

ansbile <hosts> -m <module>
ansible target1 -m ping -i inventory.txt




Ansible Playbook Commands
ansible-playbook <playbook file> -i <inventory file>
